Key - Bindings
--------------
Zoom            - ctrl + plus, minus, equel
Scollback       - shift + page_up, page_down (mouse scroll)
External Pipe   - alt + l (select url with rofi to open in browser)
                  alt + y (select url with rofi to copy to xsel)
                  alt + o (select command with rofi to copy output to xsel)

